Template: dari-compute-node/api_url
Type: string
Description: DARI server API URL
 The full URL to the DARI API endpoint (e.g., https://dari.example.com/api).

Template: dari-compute-node/api_key
Type: string
Description: API key for this compute node
 The API key assigned to this server in the DARI admin panel (Admin > Servers).

Template: dari-compute-node/management_iface
Type: select
Choices: ${choices}
Description: Management network interface
 Network adapter used for management traffic (DARI API, LDAP, all-smi).

Template: dari-compute-node/nfs_iface
Type: select
Choices: ${choices}
Description: NFS network interface
 Network adapter used for NFS data traffic.

Template: dari-compute-node/ldap_uri
Type: string
Description: LDAP server URI
 URI of the LDAP server (e.g., ldaps://dari.example.com).
 Leave blank to auto-derive from the API URL.

Template: dari-compute-node/allsmi_port
Type: string
Default: 9100
Description: all-smi API port
 Port for the all-smi API mode endpoint.
